{"version":"1.2","person":{"datePublished":"2023-12-28","name":"Aimery VI de Rochechouart Vicomte de Rochechouart","nameForms":[{"lang":"fr","fullText":"Aimery VI de Rochechouart Vicomte de Rochechouart","parts":[{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Given","value":"Aimery VI"},{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Surname","value":"de Rochechouart"},{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Suffix","value":"Vicomte de Rochechouart"}],"order":"EUROTYPIC"}],"alternateName":"Aymery VI or Aimerie VI","gender":"Male","lifespan":"1155–1230","fullLifespan":"about 1155–1230","portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/1dy4l/thumb200s.jpg","@type":"ImageObject"},"memoryArtifacts":[{"memoryType":"PHOTO","url":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7767-126693-4296-29/dist.png?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","memoryUrl":"https://www.familysearch.org/photos/artifacts/177758473","thumbnailUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7767-126693-4296-29/thumb200s.jpg?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","deepZoomUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/deepzoomcloud/dzpatron/v1/TH-7767-126693-4296-29/scale?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","headline":"rochechouart Fascé ondé et enté d'argent et de gueules de six pièces.","@type":"ImageObject"}],"birthDate":"+1155","birthPlace":{"address":"Rochechouart, Limousin, Kingdom of France","geo":{"latitude":45.75,"longitude":0.8333,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"deathDate":"+1230","deathPlace":{"address":"Rochechouart, Limousin, Kingdom of France","geo":{"latitude":45.75,"longitude":0.8333,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"userCertifiedLifeSummary":"Armoirie de la famille de Rochechouart :\n Fascé, ondé et enté d'argent et de gueules de 6 pièces.\ndevise : \nANTE MARE UNDAE\nAVANT QUE LA MER FUT AU MONDE, ROCHECHOUART PORTAIT LES ONDES\nAymeric, 6ème du nom, vicomte de Rochechouard dès l’an 1171, fonda, l’an 1202, avec son fils, le prieuré de Trezen, ordre de Grandmont, sur la paroisse des Billanges. Il était homme-lige du roi, en 1226, et tenait de lui la ville et le chastel de Rochechouard. Il épousa Luce, dame de Perusse.\nSource : \n\nAimery VI, vicomte de Rochechouart est désigné dans plusieurs titres comme fondateur du prieuré de Trézou, de l'ordre de Grandmont, en 1205.\nIl fonda, l'an 1250, le couvent des cordeliers de Saint-Junien, auquel les vicomtes de Rochechouart ont fait toujours de nombreuses donations, comme le prouve l'obituaire de ce monastère.\nSources : \n- Nobiliaire du diocèse et de la généralité de Limoges - Tome 4 – page 42 ;\n- Histoire de la maison de Rochechouart – page 72 ;\n- Acte de Mariage - Archives Départementale Haute-Vienne - Commune de PAGEAS - 3 E 112 / 2 page 144 ;\nrelevé JPR Teyssier Chalancon Mangas","sourceList":[{"title":"Foundation for Medieval Genealogy","sourceType":"DEFAULT","sourceLink":"https://fmg.ac/Projects/MedLands/LIMOUSIN.htm#AimeryIIIRochechouartdied1089","sourceUri":"QKL2-99C"},{"title":"Origines de Dynasty de Rochechouart - Racine Histoire, Aymeric IV, V, VI, VII, VIII","sourceType":"USER_UPLOADED","sourceLink":"http://familysearch.org/patron/source/photoId/187742224","sourceUri":"QKLK-VJQ"},{"title":"Fontes Nascimento, casamento, morte: http://gw.geneanet.org/adecarne?lang=fr;pz=arnaud;nz=broquet;ocz=0;p=aymery;n=de+rochechouart;oc=6","sourceType":"DEFAULT","sourceUri":"S6J3-ZXZ"}],"events":[{"name":"Birth","sources":"0","year":"1155","date":"about 1155","place":"Rochechouart, Limousin, Kingdom of France"},{"name":"TitleOfNobility","sources":"0","year":"1170","date":"from 1170 to 1230","age":"75"},{"name":"Death of Parent","sources":"0","year":"1170","date":"1170","age":"15","id":"K2YN-SGQ"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1179","date":"1179","place":"Rochechouart, Haute-Vienne, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France","age":"24","id":"LJJQ-ZMZ"},{"name":"Marriage","sources":"0","year":"1180","date":"1180","place":"Rochechouart, Haute-Vienne, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France","type":